result:
.description
    .wrapper

        template(v-for="(card, i) in page.acf ? page.acf.editor : []")

            block-article(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 1'"
                :key="i"
                :title="card.field1",
                :text="card.field2"
            )

            block-text(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 7'"
                :key="i"
                :text="card.field1"
            )

            block-video(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 8'"
                :key="i"
                :link="card.field1"
            )

            block-blockquote(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 2'"
                :key="i"
                :text="card.field1"
            )

            block-img(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 3'"
                :key="i"
                :url="card.image.url"
            )

            block-table(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 6'"
                :key="i"
                :table="card.field1"
            )

            block-list(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 4'"
                :key="i"
                :list="card.field1"
            )

            block-opinion(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 9'"
                :key="i"
                :card="card"
            )

        social-block
        
    aside.description__sidebar
        //- specifications(v-if="list.acf.editor[0].acf_fc_layout.indexOf('6') > -1" :items="list.acf.editor[0]")
        card-app
